    "title": "Saibari the difference as Morocco edge past Scotland in World Cup",
    "description": "RIYADH: Scotland spent almost 89 minutes searching for a response, but the damage had already been done. Ismael Saibari’s goal in the second minute of the game proved enough to give Morocco a 1-0 victory in Foxborough and send the Atlas Lions to the top of Group C. Saibari’s goal is now officially the fastest scored at the 2026 FIFA World Cup. Seventy-one seconds was all it",
